                  <li>‚Ä¢ Conversational AI for operators</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Multilingual support (Turkish, English, +)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-gray-300 font-semibold mb-2">Use Cases:</p>
                <ul class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
