                Vector databases (Pinecone, Weaviate), Prompt engineering frameworks
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mt-3"><strong>Recent Projects:</strong></p>
              <ul class="text-gray-400 text-xs space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Railway regulation query system (98% accuracy)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Maintenance log analysis (70% time savings)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Multi-language documentation translation</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- AI Agents -->
          <div class="bg-dark-secondary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">ü§ù AI Agents & Agent-to-Agent (A2A) Communication</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
