                <ul class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Monitoring Agents: Watch systems, detect anomalies</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Planning Agents: Optimize schedules and routes</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Execution Agents: Perform automated tasks</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Coordination Agents: Orchestrate workflows</li>
