                <li>‚Ä¢ Autonomous maintenance scheduling</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Multi-train coordination in congested networks</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Distributed resource allocation</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Self-healing system architectures</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mt-3"><strong>Technologies:</strong></p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">
                Python-based agent frameworks, MQTT for agent messaging, Kubernetes for agent deployment,
                Reinforcement learning (PPO, DQN)
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- MCP -->
          <div class="bg-dark-secondary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">üîó Model Context Protocol (MCP)</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              Seamless AI-to-Enterprise Integration
            </p>
            
            <div class="mb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-300 mb-3">
                A standardized protocol enabling AI models to interact seamlessly with enterprise software,
                databases, and external APIs without custom integration code for each system.
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-4">
              <div>
                <p class="text-gray-300 font-semibold mb-2">Our Implementation:</p>
                <ul class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Universal adapter layer for legacy systems</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Context-aware model invocation</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Secure credential management</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Request/response standardization</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Version control for model updates</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-gray-300 font-semibold mb-2">Benefits:</p>
                <ul class="text-gray-300 text-sm space-y-1 ml-4">
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Plug-and-play AI integration</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Reduced development time (60% faster)</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Consistent behavior across systems</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Easy model swapping/A-B testing</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Audit trails for AI decisions</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-dark-quaternary/50 rounded-lg p-4">
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-2"><strong>Technology Stack:</strong></p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">
                gRPC for high-performance communication, Protocol Buffers for serialization,
                OAuth2 for authentication, OpenAPI for documentation
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Big Data Analytics -->
          <div class="bg-dark-secondary/50 backdrop-blur-lg rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">üìä Big Data Analytics</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
