                  <li>‚Ä¢ Diagnostic: Why did it happen?</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Predictive: What will happen?</li>
                  <li>‚Ä¢ Prescriptive: What should we do?</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-dark-quaternary/50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
              <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-2"><strong>Specialized Analytics:</strong></p>
              <ul class="text-gray-400 text-xs space-y-1 ml-4">
                <li>‚Ä¢ Network analysis (graph algorithms)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Spatial analytics (GIS integration)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Text analytics (NLP on logs)</li>
                <li>‚Ä¢ Sensor data fusion</li>
