              <p class="text-gray-400 text-xs">
                Apache Spark (distributed processing), Apache Flink (stream processing),
                Hadoop ecosystem (HDFS, Hive), Presto (interactive queries),
                Databricks (unified analytics), Elasticsearch (search analytics)
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
